aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
LEVEL UP YOUR GAME 
Revolutionize your gaming experience with the Z2, the ultimate weapon in any gamer's arsenal. Packed with 13 customizable buttons, deep-click technology, an in-built gyroscope, tilt gestures, haptic feedback, RGB lighting, and the X1 Control Panel Software, the Z2 is your ticket to gaming supremacy. 
UNRIVALED PRECISION AND SPEED 
The 5G Pixart PAW3395 is the most advanced gaming sensor we have ever used. Paired with next-level precision, speed, responsiveness and expert tuning the Z2 is capable of 650+ ips across the whole 50 - 26,000 DPI range. It can comfortably and consistently hit the all-important 1000 Hz polling rate. 
ERGONOMICS THAT EMPOWER 
With perfectly positioned buttons and customizable caps and tilt feet, the Z2 is a finely crafted instrument that fits like a glove. Ergonomically designed to perfection and built for precision, it features side wings that reduce drag and improve control, allowing you to tilt with ease. 
CUSTOMIZE YOUR GAMEPLAY 
Customize the Z2 mouse for optimal gameplay and workflow with 13 fully customizable buttons, pressure sensors, gestures, and thousands of programmable actions. Save profiles and customizations directly to your mouse. The Z2 adapts to your style of work and play. 
OLED DISPLAY 
The Swiftpoint Z2 stands out with its unique OLED screen, providing endless customization options. You can display customized messages or show various mouse settings such as DPI and tilt angle. This feature allows you to make your mouse truly your own. 
DEEP CLICK TECHNOLOGY 
Deep Click allows you to assign multiple actions to a single button, which can be customized to streamline your gameplay. With haptic feedback, you can feel the level of deep click you have activated. Try this: Right click 25% deep to aim, 75% to lower your DPI, then 100% to fire. 
GYROSCOPE AND TILT 
The Z2 isn't just a standard mouse; it's also a controller. With its built-in accelerometer and gyroscope, it offers you true analog controls like a joystick, space mouse, or Surface Dial would. Use tilt to lean, make analog adjustments when driving, or fly a plane using the 3-Axis extender. 
X1 CONTROL PANEL 
The Z2 not only sets a new standard for computer mice, but it also raises the bar for software. Introducing the new X1 Control Panel, with a sleek design, and improved functionality. Program advanced macros or keystroke combinations into every mouse, for every game your play. 
PLAY YOUR WAY 
The X1 Control Panel is your go-to destination for customizing pre-made game and design profiles, creating your own profiles, updating firmware, and staying up-to-date with the latest features. It is available for both Windows and Mac, so you can have complete control over your Z2 experience.
